  "staticData": null,
  "description": "Webhook POST /webhook/champion-deployed (called by Evolution Monitor on champion_promoted). Pulls /api/models/champion, gates on minimum thresholds (mmlu>0.55, arc>0.50, hellaswag>0.55, gsm8k>0.40, humaneval>0.30), then POSTs DEPLOYMENT_HOOK_URL (when set), POSTs a deployment alert to /api/system/alerts, and Slack-notifies success or block reason."
